http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: has contributor agent of moving image

http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#defi.@value: Relates a resource to an agent who is a contributor to aggregate who creates a moving image resource that is embodied in an aggregate.
Relates a resource to an agent who is a contributor to aggregate who creates a musical resource that is embodied in an aggregate.
Relates a resource to an agent who is a contributor to aggregate who creates an object resource that is embodied in an aggregate.
Relates a resource to an agent who is a contributor to aggregate who creates a spoken word resource that is embodied in an aggregate.
Relates a resource to an agent who is a contributor to aggregate who creates a textual resource that is embodied in an aggregate.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about a date associated with a claim of protection under copyright or a similar regime.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: has resource designation of sequence statement

http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#defi.@value: Relates a resource to a resource statement about the designation of a sequence of a resource of a part, issue, or iteration of a diachronic resource.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to thesis and other dissertation information.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the distribution of a published resource.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about an edition to which a resource belongs.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about an interval at which the resources of parts, issues, or iterations of a diachronic resource are issued.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about a code, number, or other string, usually independent of natural language and social naming conventions, used to identify a resource.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the printing, duplicating, casting, etc., of a published resource.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about data relating to the inscription, fabrication, construction, etc., of an unpublished resource.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about the publication, release, or issuing of a resource.

Relates a resource to a resource statement about a designation for one or more regions of the world for which a videodisc or video game carrier has been encoded, indicating that playback is restricted to a device configured to decode it.
Relates a resource to a resource statement about a series to which a resource belongs and a sequence within the series.
Relates a resource to a statement appearing in a resource and deemed to be significant for users to understand how the resource represents itself.

http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#lab.@value: has resource title and responsibility statement

http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#defi.@value: Relates a resource to a resource statement about a name of a resource and the agent creating or contributing to the content of the expression embodied in a resource.
Relates a resource to a point size of the type used to represent the characters and symbols in a resource.
Relates a resource to a word or phrase that distinguishes a resource from another resource.
Relates a nomen to a scheme in which an appellation is established.

http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scop.@value: The scheme can be a value or vocabulary encoding scheme or a syntax encoding scheme.

http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#defi.@value: Relates a nomen to a set of characters or symbols with which an appellation is formed.
Relates a nomen to a resource that has an identifier for resource that consists of a group of characters from specified locations in a resource combined with a date of publication or other element.
Relates a nomen to a source in which there is evidence for the use of a nomen.
Relates a nomen to an indication of a level of authentication of the nomen of an entity.
